		{"id":"201e964ecf3114e9","type":"text","text":"![[Pasted image 20241120204933.png]]\n\n因为 $f(x)$ 连续, 所以 $m \\leq f(x) \\leq M$. 故\n$$\nm \\leq \\int^{\\dfrac{\\pi}{2}}_{0}f(x)x\\sin x \\leq M \\int^{\\dfrac{\\pi}{2}}_{0}x \\sin x  = M\n$$\n由介值定理可知, 存在 $\\xi \\in (0,\\dfrac{\\pi}{2})$, 有 $f(\\xi)= \\int^{\\frac{\\pi}{2}}_{0}f(x)x\\sin x$.\n同时, 由条件可知\n$$\nm \\leq \\dfrac{f(x_{1})+f(x_{2})}{2} \\leq M\n$$\n所以也存在 $\\zeta \\in (\\dfrac{\\pi}{2},\\pi)$, 有 $f(\\zeta) = \\int^{\\frac{\\pi}{2}}_{0}f(x)x\\sin x$, 故存在 $f'(k)=0$.\n\n","x":-497,"y":-153,"width":797,"height":653,"color":"1"},
